import sys
readline = sys.stdin.readline
T = int(readline())
for _ in range(T):
    N = int(readline())
    S = list(map(int, readline().split()))
    A = [S[0]]
    for i in range(1, N):
        s = S[i]
        a = A[i - 1]
        tmp = sorted({s + a, -s + a})
        if len(tmp) == 1 or tmp[0] < 0:
            A.append(tmp[-1])
        else:
            print(-1)
            break
    else:
        print(*A)

def loop(s, d, n):
    ans = [s]
    for i in range(1, n):
        if d[i] and s - d[i] >= 0:
            return [-1]
        s += d[i]
        ans.append(s)
    return ans
for _ in range(int(input())):
    n = int(input())
    d = list(map(int, input().split()))
    s = d[0]
    ans = loop(s, d, n)
    print(*ans, sep=' ')
